          =link_to('wardrobe', article_path(id='the_wardrobe_challenge'))
        your
        =succeed "," do
          =link_to('drawers', article_path(id='fix_your_drawers_forever'))
        and your
        =link_to('shelves', article_path(id='get_your_messy_shelves_in_shape'))
        too.

      %h2
        My new life

      %p
        I have repurposed everything I didn’t need in my wardrobe.

      %p
        It takes me minutes to get ready in the morning because I only choose from things I already know that I will wear.
        It saves me so much time and I use that time to strive for great purpose in my life.
        It helps me achieve my goals and do meaningful things that I want to do, like less laundry and more travel,
        but it all started with my wardrobe and making it have better purpose in my life for me.

      %p
        I found my purpose, it’s right here.
